N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1155.7 - Possessory lien

State Regulations

The manager shall have authority to detain any aircraft, watercraft or motor vehicle for non-payment of landing fees or storage charges
due to the authority. Notes
